00:07.907 --> 00:10.223
.

00:10.224 --> 00:12.540
.

00:13.161 --> 00:16.697
Oh, Lonely Blade, you so lonely.

00:16.699 --> 00:19.267
.

00:19.268 --> 00:21.836
.

00:21.838 --> 00:25.706
What?! The janitor is
the evil samurai president?!

00:26.275 --> 00:29.688
- That's bananas.
- Oh, come on. It was so obvious.

00:29.728 --> 00:31.979
He's been mopping in the
background of every fight scene.

00:31.981 --> 00:34.281
Look. Here he is on
the cover of the box.

00:34.283 --> 00:35.883
<i>Oh, yeah!</i>

00:35.885 --> 00:38.253
.

00:38.254 --> 00:40.621
.

00:43.226 --> 00:46.694
.

00:46.696 --> 00:48.195
Go, Lonely, go!

00:48.197 --> 00:51.365
- Do the boomerang blade again!
- Oh, come on.

00:51.367 --> 00:54.135
This is ridiculous.
Just look at their form.

00:54.137 --> 00:56.804
This is nothing like real
sword-fighting.

00:56.806 --> 00:58.839
Shh!

00:58.841 --> 01:00.107
It's just a movie, Pearl.

01:00.109 --> 01:03.344
Well, if you ever want
to see a demonstration of proper

01:03.346 --> 01:07.382
sword techniques,
I'd be happy to show you.

01:09.385 --> 01:10.351
Now?

01:11.254 --> 01:13.054
<i>All right.
In order to give a proper</i>

01:13.056 --> 01:17.925
demonstration, I'm going
to need a sparring partner.

01:17.927 --> 01:21.962
Luckily, I have the perfect
candidate right here.

01:26.202 --> 01:30.905
- Cool! Hologram Pearl!
- Ah, geez.

01:31.974 --> 01:34.942
<i>Do you wish to engage in combat?</i>

01:34.944 --> 01:37.278
Let this be the perfect battle.

01:37.280 --> 01:40.714
<i>You've already made a mistake
by challenging me.</i>

01:42.018 --> 01:43.984
We shall let our swords decide.

01:43.986 --> 01:45.119
Nerd!

01:45.121 --> 01:46.321
- Shh!
- Shh!

01:47.323 --> 01:49.323
<i>Commencing duel.</i>

01:51.000 --> 01:57.074
